ðŸ““ Tasks, boards & notes for the command-line habitat
				repo: https://github.com/klaussinani/taskbook

Overview:

$ tb --help                          -> Extra information
$ tb                                 -> Display board view
$ tb -t                              -> Create Task
$ tb -c <numbers>                    -> Check Task <numbers>
$ tb --clear                         -> Clear all checked items
$ tb -e <number>                     -> Edit task number
$ tb -p @<task number> <priority>    -> Priority update 1 normal, 2 medium, 3 high
$ tb -n                              -> Add note to the board
$ tb -d <task/note number>           -> Delete task or note

